HEADWORD: Perivitelline
<hw>Per`i*vi*tel"line</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>peri-</ets> + <ets>vitelline</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Biol.)</fld>
